But He replied and said to them, <FR>“My mother and My brethren are these who hear the word of God and do it.”<Fr>
Now it happened, on a certain day, that He got into a boat with His disciples. And He said to them, <FR>“Let us cross over to the other side of the lake<Fr><FR>.” <Fr>And they launched out.
