And He said to them, <FR>“Take nothing for <FI>your<Fi> journey, neither staffs nor bag nor bread nor money; and do not have two coats each.<Fr>
<FR>“Whatever house you enter into, stay there, and from there depart.<Fr>
<FR>And whoever will not receive you, when you go out of that city, shake off the very dust from your feet as a testimony against them.”<Fr>
