And while the people were tightly gathered together, He began to say, <FR>“This is an evil generation. It seeks a sign, and no sign will be given to it except the sign of Jonah the prophet.<Fr>
<FR>Because, as Jonah became a sign to the Ninevites, so also the Son of Man will be to this generation.<Fr>
