<FR>It is like leaven, which a woman took and hid three measures of meal inside until it was all leavened.”<Fr>
And He went through the cities and villages, teaching, and journeying toward Jerusalem.
Then one said to Him, “Lord, are there few who are saved?” And He said to them,
<FR>“Strive to enter through the narrow gate, because many, I say to you, will seek to enter in and will not be able.<Fr>
