<FR>then you will begin to say, ‘We ate and drank in Your presence, and You have taught in our streets.'<Fr>
<FR>But He will say, ‘I tell you I do not know you, where you are from. Depart from Me, all <FI>you<Fi> workers of iniquity.'<Fr>
