<FR>And the son said to him, ‘Father, I have sinned against heaven and in your sight, and am no longer worthy to be called your son.'<Fr>
<FR>“But the father said to his servants, ‘Bring out the best robe and put <FI>it<Fi> on him, and put a ring on his hand and sandals on <FI>his<Fi> feet.<Fr>
