\pard\nowidctlpar The bible cannot be \i owned\i0  by anyone as it is the words of God. Textus Receptus PTY. LTD. is the owner of the copyright concerning The King James Version 2016 (KJV 2016). The KJV 2016 is copyrighted for the sole purpose of protecting the text from alteration. The KJV 2016 text may be freely referenced and/or quoted in spoken, written, visual, or electronic formats of any kind such as, but not limited to, cassettes, Compact Disks, television, church bulletins and liturgies, or any other form of media without requesting for permission. As copyright owner, Textus Receptus PTY. LTD. grants permission for the printing and publishing of this text in any format and in any country, on the condition that the text is not altered in any way and the name King James Version 2016 or its abbreviation (KJV 2016) is supplied by way of reference or footnote in accordance with internationally recognised referencing standards.\par\
